                        Heinrichs,</rs>
                     <rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_wuerfel_QGW_II_I_1001">2. Niclas des
                        Würfels</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__kunigunde_QGW_II_I_373">3. der
                        Grundfrau</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__pilgrim_wuerfel_QGW_II_I_373">4.
                           <roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Pilgreims des Würfels, des
                        obgenanten Hainreichs des Würfel <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__heinrich_wuerfel_QGW_II_I_459">pruder</roleName>, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__klosterneuburg">chorherr</roleName> ze
                        Neunburch</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__jakob_maeserl_QGW_II_I_121">5.
                           <roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Jacobs des Meserleins</rs> , <rs type="person" ref="pe__albrecht_rampersdorfer_QGW_II_I_388">6. <roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Albrechts des Ramperstorfer</rs>.</rs></rs>
